                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060521-25-victim275 t18060521-25-viclabel137"></join>. Last Thursday night the shoes mentioned in the indictment were hanging in my back parlour, I saw them there at eleven o'clock when I went to bed; about a few minutes after seven 
